text: Idelbakovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Kazanbulaksky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,283 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 87 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Idelbakovo
